casebody.data:
CROSSROADS INVESTORS
v.
FEDERAL NATIONAL MORTGAGE ASSOCIATION S234737 Supreme Court of California October 19, 2016

Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The above-entitled matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Third Appellate District, for reconsideration in light of the decision in Baral v. Sc h nitt (2016) 1 Cal.5th 376, 205 Cal.Rptr.3d 475, 376 P.3d 604. The Reporter of Decisions is directed not to publish the Court of Appeal opinion in this matter, filed April 14, 2016, in the Official Reports.
